questions.question: For at least 15 frames, an object o0 is at the bottom of the frame and to the left of another object o1, at the same time, a rubber object o2 is to the right of o1. Next, for at least 15 frames, o1 is made of rubber. Finally, for a duration of at least 10 frames, o1 is in front of o2, and o2 is on the right side of the frame.
questions.dsl: Duration((Bottom(o0), LeftOf(o0, o1), Material(o2, 'rubber'), RightOf(o2, o1)), 15); Duration(Material(o1, 'rubber'), 15); Duration((FrontOf(o1, o2), Right(o2)), 10)

questions.question: For at least 15 frames, an object o0 is to the left of another object o1 and simultaneously o1 is to the right of o0. Then, for a duration of at least 10 frames, o0 is on the left side of the video frame, is made of rubber, and o1 is shaped like a cube. Finally, for at least 5 frames, o2 is far away from o0, while o1 is on the right side of the video frame.
questions.dsl: Duration((LeftOf(o0, o1), RightOf(o1, o0)), 15); Duration((Left(o0), Material(o0, 'rubber'), Shape(o1, 'cube')), 10); Duration((Far(o2, o0, 3.0), Right(o1)), 5)

questions.question: For at least 15 frames, an object o0 is far away from another object o1, and a third object o2 is at the top of the frame. Then, o0 is behind o2, o1 is at the bottom of the frame and in front of o0, and o2 is made of rubber. Finally, o2 is green for a duration of at least 10 frames.
questions.dsl: Duration((Far(o0, o1, 3.0), Top(o2)), 15); (Behind(o0, o2), Bottom(o1), FrontOf(o1, o0), Material(o2, 'rubber')); Duration(Color(o2, 'green'), 10)

questions.question: For at least 5 frames, an object o0 is behind another object o1, while a third object o2 is made of rubber and o1 is at the top of the frame. Following that, for at least 10 frames, o2 is far from o0 and is in front of o1, and o1 is on the right side of the frame. Finally, o0 is purple and on the left side of the frame.
questions.dsl: Duration((Behind(o0, o1), Material(o2, 'rubber'), Top(o1)), 5); Duration((Far(o2, o0, 3.0), FrontOf(o2, o1), Right(o1)), 10); (Color(o0, 'purple'), Left(o0))

questions.question: For at least 15 frames, a rubber object o2 is somewhere in the frame while a sphere o0 is in front of another object o1. After that, o2 is on the right side of the frame and far from o0, o1 is on the left side of the frame and close to o0.
questions.dsl: Duration((FrontOf(o0, o1), Material(o2, 'rubber'), Shape(o0, 'sphere')), 15); (Far(o2, o0, 3.0), Left(o1), Near(o1, o0, 1.0), Right(o2))

questions.question: A gray object o0 is far away from another object o1 for at least 5 frames. Afterward, o1 is to the right of a third object o2, o1 is on the right side of the frame, and o0 is at the top of the frame. Finally, for a duration of at least 15 frames, o0 is on the left side of the frame and o2 is made of rubber.
questions.dsl: Duration((Color(o0, 'gray'), Far(o0, o1, 3.0)), 5); (RightOf(o1, o2), Right(o1), Top(o0)); Duration((Left(o0), Material(o2, 'rubber')), 15)

questions.question: For at least 15 frames, an object o0 is to the left of another object o1. Subsequently, for at least 10 frames, o1 is in front of a third object o2, while o0 is on the left side of the video frame. Then, in a further sequence lasting at least 10 frames, o0 is behind o2, o0 is far from o2, o2 is made of rubber, o1 is on the right side of the frame, and o1 is shaped like a cylinder.
questions.dsl: Duration(LeftOf(o0, o1), 15); Duration((FrontOf(o1, o2), Left(o0)), 10); Duration((Behind(o0, o2), Far(o0, o2, 3.0), Material(o2, 'rubber'), Right(o1), Shape(o1, 'cylinder')), 10)

questions.question: For at least 5 frames, an object o0 is far away from another object o1. Next, for a duration of at least 5 frames, o0 is a cylinder and to the left of o1, which is blue, while an object o2 is at the top of the frame. Finally, o2 is near o1, positioned on the right side of the frame, and o1 is at the top of the frame.
questions.dsl: Duration(Far(o0, o1, 3.0), 5); Duration((Color(o1, 'blue'), LeftOf(o0, o1), Shape(o0, 'cylinder'), Top(o2)), 5); (Near(o2, o1, 1.0), Right(o2), Top(o1))

questions.question: For a duration of at least 10 frames, an object o0 is at the bottom of the video frame and to the left of both objects o1 and o2. Subsequently, for at least 15 frames, o1 is to the left of o2. Finally, o2 is behind o0 and far from o1, o1 is shaped like a sphere, and o2 is shaped like a cylinder.
questions.dsl: Duration((Bottom(o0), LeftOf(o0, o1), LeftOf(o0, o2)), 10); Duration(LeftOf(o1, o2), 15); (Behind(o2, o0), Far(o2, o1, 3.0), Shape(o1, 'sphere'), Shape(o2, 'cylinder'))

questions.question: Two objects o0 and o2 are both in front of another object o1 for at least 5 frames. Then, for at least 10 frames, o2 is red and o1 is made of rubber, and o1 is to the right of o2. Finally, for at least 15 frames, o0 is far from o2, and o1 is on the right side.
questions.dsl: Duration((FrontOf(o0, o1), FrontOf(o2, o1)), 5); Duration((Color(o2, 'red'), Material(o1, 'rubber'), RightOf(o1, o2)), 10); Duration((Far(o0, o2, 3.0), Right(o1)), 15)
